314
00:13:26,985 --> 00:13:29,536
Look at this.

315
00:13:29,538 --> 00:13:33,540
"Photos of Wolowitz family
before father left forever."

316
00:13:36,544 --> 00:13:40,547
Check out nine-year-old Howie
