344
00:14:52,070 --> 00:14:53,486
and then we don't tell you

345
00:14:53,488 --> 00:14:55,938
which one it is,
you will forever be

346
00:14:55,940 --> 00:14:58,458
in a state
of epistemic ambivalence.

347
00:14:58,460 --> 00:14:59,542
Yeah.

